al illusions, his works thereby make reality strangely unreal.\",\"detail\":\"Joanie Lemercier is a French artist who co-founded the visual label AntiVJ in 2008 and Studio Joanie Lemercier in 2013.\",\"slug\":\"joanie-lemercier\",\"perform\":null,\"time_perform\":null,\"stage\":null,\"description\":null,\"_token\":\"u60t1BVrMz7MtSgJy6fB7AjPKtjBk6GoTgIpehLK\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8000\\/painkillers\\/lineups\"}','2019-09-13 13:21:00','2019-09-13 13:21:00'),(1267,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','127.0.0.1','[]','2019-09-13 13:21:01','2019-09-13 13:21:01'),(1268,1,'painkillers/lineups/create','GET','127.0.0.1','{\"_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-09-13 13:21:05','2019-09-13 13:21:05'),(1269,1,'painkillers/lineups','POST','127.0.0.1','{\"name\":\"Kinara Dharma\",\"lineups_type\":\"Artist\",\"bio\":\"Kinara Darma is an initiative founded by Yoga Prathama & Utari Intan in 2016. This project was initiated to connect different energies and transform it into an artwork; a positive impact.\",\"detail\":\"Through their latest work \\u201cWe Are Here\\u201d Kinara Darma seeks to unravel human interaction in our everyday lives. This artwork invites audience on a journey to revisit the purpose of our being through experiments with sound, words, and visuals to represent the notion of harmony using elements that each represents our organic, borderless, yet interconnected society.\",\"slug\":\"kinara-darma\",\"perform\":null,\"time_perform\":null,\"stage\":null,\"description\":null,\"_token\":\"u60t1BVrMz7MtSgJy6fB7AjPKtjBk6GoTgIpehLK\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8000\\/painkillers\\/lineups\"}','2019-09-13 13:23:32','2019-09-13 13:23:32'),(1270,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','127.0.0.1','[]','2019-09-13 13:23:33','2019-09-13 13:23:33'),(1271,1,'painkillers/lineups/create','GET','127.0.0.1','{\"_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-09-13 13:24:30','2019-09-13 13:24:30'),(1272,1,'painkillers/lineups','POST','127.0.0.1','{\"name\":\"Sembilan Matahari\",\"line