\\u201d to depict the adaptive nature of borders (time and space). Through the use of 3-dimensional visuals installation made of 2-dimensional shapes formed by lines of strings, this piece offers immersive experience that invites viewers to see the world with a new perspective.\",\"detail\":\"Through \\u201cString Composition - Series 5\\u201d, Rubi aims to reawaken our awareness of space. Responding to human interaction through movements and sound, this installation is built using pieces of 2 Dimensional shape formed using lines of strings. Transparent yet sturdy and solid when viewed from a certain angle, the shapes are designed to have the depth to capture light projections and movements creating 3 Dimensional visuals, rethinking the definition of scaled borders - both of time and distance.\",\"slug\":\"rubi-roesli\",\"perform\":null,\"time_perform\":null,\"stage\":null,\"description\":null,\"_token\":\"e2rHiOEB9ClnMTk8Klxch8JSEpDxK6u2Oz2jzPE9\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-09-20 01:47:16','2019-09-20 01:47:16'),(1700,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.23','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups?\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-09-20 01:47:17','2019-09-20 01:47:17'),(1701,1,'painkillers/lineups/create','GET','172.18.106.23','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/create?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-09-20 01:48:38','2019-09-20 01:48:38'),(1702,1,'painkillers/lineups','POST','172.18.106.23','{\"name\":\"NOTANLAB\",\"lineups_type\":\"Sight\",\"installation_name\":\"c o l o ( u r ) & c a p t ( u r ) e\",\"bio\":\"Notanlab is a Bandung-based digital creative whose practice offers an unison of technology, science, art and design.\\r\\nInspired by the interactions around human, they created two installations called \\u201ccapt(ur)e\\u201d and \\u201ccolo(ur)\\u201d for Wave of Tomorrow. These pieces were made to invite viewers to analyze how human emotions and memories were made to be adaptive towards ever-changing daily experiences they encounter.\",\"detail\":\"Forming a creative expression through a combination of technology, science, art and design, Notanlab, Bandung-based digital creative shapes their work by experimental practice. Inspired by the interactions that occur around humans, they created two installations called \\u201ccapt(ur)e\\u201d and \\u201ccolo(ur)\\u201d. Presented in the form of a robotic arm installation which symbolized as a human hand, \\u201ccapt(ur)e\\u201d answers the concern of our dependence on storing memory through technology, whereas, \\u201ccolo(ur)\\u201d is an interactive installation that combines mural art and smartphones as a means to find out individual emotions through color. \\r\\nBoth of these works will invite audiences to engage with the experiences that they encounter in everyday life.\",\"slug\":\"notanlab\",\"perform\":null,\"time_perform\":null,\"stage\":null,\"description\":null,\"_token\":\"e2rHiOEB9ClnMTk8Klxch8JSEpDxK6u2Oz2jzPE9\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-09-20 01:52:24','2019-09-20 01:52:24'),(1703,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.23','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups?\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-09-20 01:52:24','2019-09-20 01:52:24'),(1704,1,'painkillers/lineups/create','GET','172.18.106.23','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/create?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-09-20 01:53:03','2019-09-20 01:53:03'),(1705,1,'painkillers/lineups','POST','172.18.106.23','{\"name\":\"MOTION BEAST\",\"lineups_type\":\"Sight\",\"installation_name\":\"Mercusuar\",\"bio\":\"Motionbeast is a Bandung-based creative studio that specializes in fusing art and technology into experimental work, from animation, CG and visual effects, interactive installation, to data visualization.\\r\\nBased on their vision to create immersive work for viewers, Motionbeast presents \\u201cMercusuar\\u201d. Emphasizing on human response towards visuals, this installation projects lights and colors into space to depict how human adapts to their surro