s, this installation projects lights and colors into space to depict how human adapts to their surroundings and simultenously discovers new experiences.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"QqPHys10VqBhyXdQa7KgNDwVLUzjZ7SgT2MmlR1O\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/36\":null}','2019-10-31 02:40:43','2019-10-31 02:40:43'),(2326,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.56','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-10-31 02:40:43','2019-10-31 02:40:43'),(2327,1,'painkillers/lineups/37/edit','GET','172.18.106.56','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/37\\/edit?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-10-31 02:40:48','2019-10-31 02:40:48'),(2328,1,'painkillers/lineups/37','PUT','172.18.106.56','{\"name\":\"U VISUAL\",\"lineups_type\":\"Sight\",\"installation_name\":\"Infinite Loop\",\"bio\":\"<p>UVisual is a Bandung-based interdisciplinary digital art studio who is known for their motion graphics specialty, ranging from video mapping, virtual reality to augmented reality.<\\/p>\",\"detail\":\"<p>Inspired by the arrangement of solar system, UVisual came up with a new work called \\u201cInfinite Loop\\u201d. <\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"u-visual\",\"perform\":null,\"time_perform\":null,\"stage\":null,\"description\":\"<p>By incorporating audio and visual elements to represent psychology energy, this work depicts wide perspective of human\'s role in the world and invites viewers to be adaptive towards the change that surrounds them.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"QqPHys10VqBhyXdQa7KgNDwVLUzjZ7SgT2MmlR1O\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/37\":null}','2019-10-31 02:41:22','2019-10-31 02:41:22'),(2329,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.56','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-10-31 02:41:23','2019-10-31 02:41:23'),(2330,1,'painkillers/lineups/38/edit','GET','172.18.106.56','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lin