cDentum Dansa Bawah Tanah\\u201d. The unit kept exploring new styles and has released a remix of The Hydrant\\u2019s \\u201cBali Bandidos\\u201d & participated in Dekadenz\\u2019s \\u201cThemes for Divided Tribes Vol.1\\u201d EP in 2018.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"v3UlMI2QlQuTFa2jv8rmD4MHMcrrt9CUh85fHmAO\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/48\":null}','2019-11-09 20:57:51','2019-11-09 20:57:51'),(3414,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-11-09 20:57:51','2019-11-09 20:57:51'),(3415,1,'painkillers/lineups/50/edit','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/50\\/edit?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 20:58:30','2019-11-09 20:58:30'),(3416,1,'painkillers/lineups/50','PUT','172.18.106.20','{\"name\":\"Random Brothers\",\"lineups_type\":\"Show\",\"installation_name\":null,\"bio\":\"<p>Random Brothers are actual brothers Randy Danistha and Nara Anindyaguna, and their music explores electronic sound with techno as their main genre.<\\/p>\",\"detail\":\"<p>Made out of their passion towards electronic music, this unit offers a bold character that differentiates them from other electronic units in the local scene.<\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"random-brothers\",\"perform\":\"2019-12-23\",\"time_perform\":\"22:00:00\",\"stage\":null,\"description\":\"<p>Using modular synthesizer, and inspired by random things, Random Brothers constantly explore new styles through their epic compositions that invites listeners into a new world.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"v3UlMI2QlQuTFa2jv8rmD4MHMcrrt9CUh85fHmAO\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/50\":null}','2019-11-09 20:59:03','2019-11-09 20:59:03'),(3417,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-11-09 20:59:03','2019-11-09 20:59:03'),(3418,1,'painkillers/lineups/51/edit','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/51\\/edit?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 20:59:39','2019-11-09 20:59:39'),(3419,1,'painkillers/lineups/51','PUT','172.18.106.20','{\"name\":\"Dekadenz\",\"lineups_type\":\"Show\",\"installation_name\":null,\"bio\":\"<p>Dekadenz is an underground music collective consisting of renowned DJs\\/producers Aditya Permana, Jonathan Kusuma and Ridwan Susanto.<\\/P>\",\"detail\":\"<p>Created under a common love for left-field music, this unit offers a place for those who love crazy beats and primitive electronic sounds.<\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"dekadenz\",\"perform\":\"2019-12-24\",\"time_perform\":\"22:00:00\",\"stage\":null,\"description\":\"<p>Known for distinct style and character, Dekadenz has set the bar high in the local party scene through their events and legendary guest DJs, bringing acts such as Vladimir Ivkovic and Cosmo Vitelli to Indonesia. Aside being the purveyor of underground parties, this unit also explore new styles through an EP series called \\u201cThemes for Divided Tribes\\u201d.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"v3UlMI2QlQuTFa2jv8rmD4MHMcrrt9CUh85fHmAO\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/51\":null}','2019-11-09 21:00:14','2019-11-09 21:00:14'),(3420,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-11-09 21:00:14','2019-11-09 21:00:14'),(3421,1,'painkillers/lineups/60/edit','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/60\\/edit?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 21:01:33','2019-11-09 21:01:33'),(3422,1,'painkillers/lineups/60','PUT','172.18.106.58','{\"name\":\"Gabber Modus Operandi\",\"lineups_type\":\"Show\",\"installation_name\":null,\"bio\":\"<p>Gabber Modus Operandi (GMO) is Kasimyn (Kas) and Ican Harem, a Denpasar-based experimental duo whose latest work, \\u201cHOXXXYA\\u201d is inspired by various local influences - the metal and noise scene in Denpasar, spirits of Dangdut Koplo, and gamelan sounds. <\\/P>\",\"detail\":\"<p>While Kas was known as a singer in a punk Jakarta-based band called United by Haircuts, Ican was in a band called Cangkang Serigala and explored the mediums of visual art and fashion. <\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"gabber-modus-operandi\",\"perform\":\"2019-12-29\",\"time_perform\":\"22:00:00\",\"stage\":null,\"description\":\"<p>Both characters then decided to create a new style - Gabber Modus Operandi. In this unit, Kas is DJing while Harem is screaming and dancing where their synergy creates visceral sounds: a combination of punk, noise, dangdut, traditional music, and sacred rituals.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"v3UlMI2QlQuTFa2jv8rmD4MHMcrrt9CUh85fHmAO\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/60\":null}','2019-11-09 21:02:00','2019-11-09 21:02:00'),(3423,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-11-09 21:02:00','2019-11-09 21:02:00'),(3424,1,'painkillers/lineups/71/edit','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/71\\/edit?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 21:03:16','2019-11-09 21:03:16'),(3425,1,'painkillers/lineups/71','PUT','172.18.106.58','{\"name\":\"Petra Sihombing\",\"lineups_type\":\"Show\",\"installation_name\":null,\"bio\":\"<p>Petra Sihombing is a pop musician whose character landed him many projects both as a soloist and music producer. He has collaborated with notable names in the industry to produce their music, from Kunto Aji, Vidi Aldiano, Incognito, Coldiac, Hindia, to rapper Iwa K.<\\/p>\",\"detail\":\"<p>Although his first full-length \\u201cMine\\u201d (2014) was a pop acoustic album, his latest album \\u201c1\\/4\\u201d (2018) offers energetic electronic sounds, that shows how Petra has been experimenting with a new style to produce fresh and appealing tunes.<\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"petra-sihombing\",\"perform\":\"2019-12-23\",\"time_perform\":\"21:00:00\",\"stage\":null,\"description\":\"<p>Not stopping there, he also released his latest single \\u201cBiji\\u201d in 2019 with colloquial lyrics and an intimate approach that shows him as a versatile and promising act you need to watch out for.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"v3UlMI2QlQuTFa2jv8rmD4MHMcrrt9CUh85fHmAO\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/lineups\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/71\":null}','2019-11-09 21:04:31','2019-11-09 21:04:31'),(3426,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\":null}','2019-11-09 21:04:31','2019-11-09 21:04:31'),(3427,1,'painkillers/content','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/content?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 21:04:37','2019-11-09 21:04:37'),(3428,1,'painkillers/content/create','GET','172.18.106.58','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/content\\/create?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 21:04:59','2019-11-09 21:04:59'),(3429,1,'painkillers/content','POST','172.18.106.20','{\"id_lineups\":\"71\",\"media_type\":\"Photos\",\"title\":\"petra-sihombing\",\"tagline\":null,\"desc\":null,\"status\":\"on\",\"_token\":\"v3UlMI2QlQuTFa2jv8rmD4MHMcrrt9CUh85fHmAO\",\"_previous_\":\"https:\\/\\/staging.waveoftomorrow.id\\/painkillers\\/content\",\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/content\":null}','2019-11-09 21:05:46','2019-11-09 21:05:46'),(3430,1,'painkillers/content','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/content\":null}','2019-11-09 21:05:46','2019-11-09 21:05:46'),(3431,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 21:06:11','2019-11-09 21:06:11'),(3432,1,'painkillers/lineups/71/edit','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups\\/71\\/edit?_pjax\":\"#pjax-container\"}','2019-11-09 21:06:18','2019-11-09 21:06:18'),(3433,1,'painkillers/lineups','GET','172.18.106.20','{\"\\/\\/painkillers\\/lineups