INSERT INTO `faq` VALUES (2,'Where\'s the Wave of Tomorrow venue?','where-is-the-place','The event will be held at The Tribata grand ballroom, Dharmawangsa Street III, South Jakarta',1,'2019-09-13 13:49:56','2019-10-25 12:34:43'),(3,'What will i see at this event?','will-i-see','Wave of Tomorrow presents works and installations from distinguished artists and collectives in Indonesia and International. Visitors can enjoy a variety of artistic expressions through technology media, lights and immersive and interactive sounds. The Wave of Tomorrow will also have several musical performances that can be enjoyed by visitors. Get ready to be inspired.',1,'2019-09-13 13:55:36','2019-09-13 13:55:36'),(4,'What\'s Wave of Tomorrow?','What\'s-Wave-of-Tomorrow?','Wave of Tomorrow is a new media art exhibition which displays contemporary artworks with technology elements. Wave of Tomorrow is giving an Art and Technology Experience Ahead of Its Time.',1,'2019-09-13 15:28:56','2019-10-25 12:38:05'),(5,'When will Wave of Tomorrow Start and End?',NULL,'Wave of tomorrow will be started from 20th - 29th December 2019.',1,'2019-09-13 15:32:42','2019-11-07 10:43:55'),(6,'Can I know the detailed rundown?','Can-I-know-the-detailed-rundown?','Find out the detailed rundown <a href=\"/schedule/\">here.</a>',1,'2019-09-18 22:59:41','2019-11-07 12:43:35'),(7,'Who\'s the lineup?','Who\'s-the-lineup?','We invite national and international artists. Know more the lineup <a href=\"/lineups/\">here.</a>',1,'2019-09-18 23:02:48','2019-11-07 12:43:55'),(9,'Is Wave of Tomorrow open for public?','Is-Wave-of-Tomorrow-open-for-public?','This event is open for ages 18 years and over. However, due to safety considerations, we do not allow pregnant women, children under 18, elderly, and people who are sensitive to bright light to attend this event.',1,'2019-09-18 23:04:45','2019-10-25 12:37:09'),(10,'Where can i get the ticket?','Where-can-i-get-the-ticket?','You can buy the ticket on the venue. We encourage you to make a purchase first prior coming to the event for your convenience. Upon arrival, make sure to show your valid ID along with the <a href=\"/#homepageTicket\">e-ticket.</a>',1,'2019-09-18 23:05:53','2019-11-08 14:09:34'),(11,'Can i go directly to the exhibition only with an e-ticket?','Can-i-go-directly-to-the-exhibition-only-with-an-e-ticket?','E-ticket is not an entry ticket, you have to exchange your e-ticket to an entry ticket in the ticket box by showing your ID. Make sure the name on the e-ticket is the same as the ID.',1,'2019-09-18 23:08:47','2019-09-18 23:08:47'),(12,'Are visitors allowed to buy tickets directly in the exhibition without reservations?','Are-visitors-allowed-to-buy-tickets-directly-in-the-exhibition-without-reservations?','Visitors can come directly to the exhibition venue without purchasing a ticket in advance. However, we will prioritize entry to e-ticket holders.',1,'2019-09-18 23:09:51','2019-09-18 23:09:51'),(15,'Can i go in and out of the exhibition on the same day?','Can-i-go-in-and-out-of-the-exhibition-on-the-same-day?','Of course, please back to the entrance and show the ticket to the committee at the entrance to allow you to the venue.',1,'2019-09-18 23:13:39','2019-09-18 23:13:39'),(16,'How do I get there considering the odd-even traffic policy?','How-do-I-get-there-considering-the-odd-even-traffic-policy?','The odd-even traffic policy is enforced on weekdays from 7 to 10 AM and 4 to 9 PM. \r\nAside from major arterial road, the policy is also applied at Jalan Fatmawati and Jalan Panglima Polim. So, in order to reach the venue, you may want to access alternative route via Jalan Pangeran Antasari.',1,'2019-10-17 11:28:53','2019-10-17 11:28:53'),(17,'How about another transport options?','How-about-another-transport-options?','There are many ways to reach the venue, you can use online transportation services, taxi or public transportation. By typing The Tribrata on location search, you can easily get to the venue via online transportation services. If you use public transportation, you can get on the Transjakarta bus MR3 or 1E and stop at Blok A MRT Station.',1,'2019-10-17 11:30:19','2019-10-17 11:30:19'),(18,'Is there any age restriction?','Is-there-any-age-restriction?','All visitors are required 18+ and must show ID (KTP, SIM, Passport) at the entrance.',1,'2019-10-17 11:31:49','2019-11-08 14:11:54'),(19,'Is it safe for pregnant women to come?','Is-it-safe-for-pregnant-women-to-come?','High decibel noise, epilepsy-inducing lights and smokes in the area may harmful for pregnant women. For the safety of both mother and baby, pregnant women are prohibited to enter the premise.',1,'2019-10-17 11:32:55','2019-10-17 19:58:03');
